name: I'm not "Finn", I'm "Niti"
description:
"UTOPIA" is a cartoon project (until then never finished) that made me find the concept and aesthetics of my art.
 is this the 8/? "UTOPIC PROFILE" season drawings - 
the eyes are always the same, the light seems to come from a single universal point and the character is always in utopia, living in utopia... (SPECIAL EDITION) I'm not "Finn", I'm "Niti"
